<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset the password for your account (<strong>{{email}}</strong>).</p>
<a href="{{url}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
<hr class="divider" />
<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;color:#71717a;">{{url}}</p>
<p>This link expires in <strong>1 hour</strong>. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password won't change.</p>
